Reservations are welcome for all party sizes! We happily accommodate groups of up to 20 through OpenTable. For parties larger than 20, please give us a call.
Please note that we have tables specifically reserved for walk-ins.
On Taco Tuesdays, we only accept reservations for large parties 7 or more.
